research/history/logs/agent_action_0295.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"扩展兼容新结构 probe：`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的最终重构为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i^{sh,1} b_i^{sh,1} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r1(x))} α_j^{sh,2} b_j^{sh,2} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r2(x))} Σ_{m∈S_e^τ(r2(x))} α_{e,m} b_{e,m} + Σ_{u∈S_res(r3(x))} γ_u c_u，其中 r1/r2/r3 是逐级 residual。两层 shared residual coarse stage、PK-routed expert cleanup 与最后的 tiny global residual cleanup 都只访问静态向量库并做有限加权和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在 r294 已显出较好 exceed 的 dual-shared PK scaffold 上再加一个很小的全局 residual tail-cleanup，能比现有 dual-shared PK 更强地压住 hard-token exceed。","summary":"已实际新增并集成 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual`，只修改 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。该 family 是对 r294 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的结构升级：保留双 shared coarse + PK cleanup，只再追加一个 tiny factorized residual cleanup。按本地 exact-string smoke 与 cost 估计，在继承 r294 的 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 配置下 total_cost_ratio 约 `0.13x`，仍在当前目标带内；因此本轮是一次 matched-cost 附近、明确面向降低 exceed 的 scaffold-upgrade probe。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"风险很直接：`cost≈0.13x` 已经要求 exceed 至少接近 `0.09~0.10` 才有机会逼近阶段目标，交换率门槛很高。如果这轮 exceed 只是比 r294 小幅下降几个点，仍不够支撑主线；但它是当前最贴近 winning scaffold 的高信息增量升级之一，值得用一轮回答。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["已落盘新增 family：`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual`，完成了 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch/class 接线。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计：selection_ratio≈0.09，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.13；处于当前允许的 matched-objective 探索带。","该 family 的结构语义是：dual shared residual coarse stage 吃主干，PK experts 做中层 cleanup，tiny factorized residual head 做尾部 cleanup；与 r294 相比，信息增量集中在 hard-token tail-cleanup 机制。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮 exceed 明显低于 r294 且 objective 改善，再以该 family 为 anchor 做一次极小幅 knee 校准，例如 `STAGE1_RATIO`。","若本轮 objective 仍无改善，则说明在 dual-shared PK scaffold 上追加 tiny global residual cleanup 的交换率不足，后续应停止继续叠加同类 cleanup 层。","若本轮出现 sanity 或 registration 异常，优先按 exact architecture string 回查 config whitelist / dispatch / class reachable 性，而不要把问题误判成训练质量结论。"],"reference_round":294}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0286.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(x)} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e^\u03c4(x)} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\u3002\u5176\u4e2d `{b_{e,j}}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\uff0c`E_pk(x)` \u7531\u4e24\u8def product-key router \u9009\u51fa\u5c11\u91cf experts\uff0cexpert \u5185\u518d\u7528 JumpReLU \u5f62\u6210\u5c40\u90e8 support\uff1b\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\u4ecd\u662f\u201cproduct-key \u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\u7684\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r282 \u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u5207\u5230 `product_key_expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `NUM_EXPERTS=2048, K=32, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u505a\u4e00\u4e2a clean matched control probe\uff1a\u6700\u8fd1 2048-scaffold \u4e0a\u7684 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u90fd\u6ca1\u628a objective \u62c9\u4f4e\uff0c\u5f53\u524d\u66f4\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u662f incumbent \u7684\u6536\u76ca\u5230\u5e95\u6765\u81ea always-on shared coarse \u4e3b\u5e72\u672c\u8eab\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u4e3b\u8981\u6765\u81ea 2048 many-tiny PK capacity\u3002\u5df2\u6709\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5 2048 plain-PK recipe \u7684 total_cost_ratio \u7ea6\u4e3a `0.09x`\uff0c\u4f4e\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d incumbent \u7684 `0.10x`\uff1b\u5982\u679c exceed_alpha_0.50 \u80fd\u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `0.18` \u5de6\u53f3\uff0c\u5c31\u6709\u673a\u4f1a\u5728\u53