research/history/logs/agent_round_0278.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s(h(x))} α_{s,i}^{sh}(h(x)) b_{s,i}^{sh} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(r_sh(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是低秩 shared bottleneck，{b_{s,i}^{sh}} 是两个静态 shared coarse 子库，r_sh(x)=x-Σ_sΣ_i α_{s,i}^{sh}b_{s,i}^{sh}，{B_e} 是静态 PK-routed expert 子库，E_pk(·) 由 low-rank hidden 上的 left/right product-key 路由选出少量 experts，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared coarse 子库查表 + PK expert 选择 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，不依赖动态字典，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r263 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` 切到新 family `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，用极轻的 dual low-rank shared coarse branch 替代 plain PK 的无主干设置，同时保留 full-expert PK cleanup，能够在 exact `total_cost_ratio=0.082427978515625` 的近同成本档位比 r277 的 single-shared lowrank 变体显著更稳住 exceed，并争取在保持低成本的同时压低 exceed_alpha_0.50 到 `0.19357784271240236` 以下以击败 r263。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在约 `0.08243x` 下明显优于 r263，并接近或击败 r266，则下一轮应留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125`，测试更轻 shared split 是否能进一步提升 low-cost objective。","如果该 family 只比 r277 好、但仍明显输给 plain PK 或 incumbent，则记录为“dual low-rank shared coarse 修复了 single-shared lowrank 的容量不足，但 lowrank shared family 仍不够强”，后续不要继续在这条线做低信息细扫。","如果该 family 仍明显失败，则可更果断地下调“lowrank shared coarse + PK cleanup”整条方向优先级，把预算转向其他真正改变 cleanup 语义的新结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，真实改动文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`