smoke。主要风险是即便 shared coarse 翻倍，lowrank shared 表达仍可能不够，导致 exceed 仍远高于 target；但这轮会以很低的额外成本给出一个高信息量结论。","summary":"已新增并接通 `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r263 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，直接裁决“更厚的 low-rank shared coarse + full-expert PK cleanup”能否在 `0.08243x` 的低成本档位修复 r277 的 exceed 崩塌。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
