research/history/logs/agent_round_0281.stdout.log:1632:research/history/results.tsv:277:r276_1775046246	1775046246	ok	archive	0.1581931710243225	0.174731	0.284106	458752.000000	0.109375	294912.000000	0.070312	163840.000000	0.039062	32	dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0276/round0276_standard_1775045606_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k32_20260401_201333	c17c194be2a4ff6418cfef9140bdfbdfe759e803			已新增并接通 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r275 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，直接裁决“更厚 shared coarse 主干 + 按难度可变 1-or-2 PK cleanup path”能否在与 dual-shared fixed-AE 完全同成本的 `0.109375x` 档位继续显著压低 exceed。	这轮符合当前阶段约束。最近两轮 r274-r275 都停留在同一 dual-shared family 内，且 objective 仍未接近 incumbent；按策略此时应优先换结构槽位，而不是继续补 `STAGE1_RATIO` 近邻点。选择 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 而不是继续在 dual-shared 上做 `0.125/0.375` 分裂点，是因为它直接测试当前高优先级方向“variable-active path by difficulty”，同时完全建立在已有 winning scaffold 的近同成本升级上。代码侧仅新增最小 family，并完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、override allowlist、compatibility registry 与 exact-string smoke；没有新增 tunable key，因此不需要改 `config_resolution`、`runner` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。主要风险是 adaptive active 在单-shared 版本上曾给过弱负信号；但 dual-shared scaffold 已把 coarse 主干抬强，当前最有价值的问题正是这是否能让 difficulty-aware cleanup 真正发挥作用。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0276_standard_1775045606.log
