research/history/logs/agent_round_0297.stdout.log:1346:research/history/logs/agent_action_0291.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"直接兼容 probe：`dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的最终重构可写为 x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s(x)} α_{s,i}^{sh} b_{s,i}^{sh} + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j}，其中两路 always-on shared 静态子库先吸收 coarse 主干，随后 product-key router 按 token 难度自适应启用 1 或 2 个静态 expert 子库做 JumpReLU cleanup。该形式仍能直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态子库查表 + 加权求和推理链路，因此兼容性判定为直接兼容。主假设是：在 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的 stronger coarse scaffold 上接入 difficulty-aware variable-active cleanup，可能比已测试的单 shared adaptive 版本更能压低 hard-token exceed。","summary":"从 r279 做单变量 architecture switch 到 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。这不是回到低信息细扫，而是沿当前最相关的 shared+PK scaffold 测试“更厚 shared coarse + variable-active residual cleanup”这一结构升级。按本地烟测与 cost 估计，`NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375` 下 total_cost_ratio 约 `0.11x`，处于 matched-objective 带；若该 family 不能在近同成本下明显降低 exceed，就可以把这条 variable-active dual-shared 支线一并降级。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"风险在于 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 先前已给过负信号，而且当前 cost proxy 对 adaptive path 的计费与 dual_shared PK 基本相同，因此这轮几乎完全是在赌 exceed 改善。如果 exceed 仍停留在 `~0.16+`，这条线就不值得继续主导预算。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计（以 r279 配置为 anchor）：selection_ratio≈0.07，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.11，与 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 同量级。","`dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 尚未在当前 target 上得到真实 objective 证据；本轮的价值在于回答 variable-active cleanup 接到 dual shared scaffold 上是否值得继续。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮在近同成本下把 exceed 明显压到 `<=0.15` 一带，再以本 family 为 anchor 单变量检查 `NUM_EXPERTS 1024→2048` 是否能继续放缓 hard-token exceed。","若本轮 objective 仍不优于 incumbent，说明现有 adaptive-active 语义不足以改善 low-K tradeoff，后续应转向真正新的 cleanup 机制，而不是继续扫 adaptive path 邻域。","若本轮出现运行异常或配置不符，优先核对 round config / checkpoint config 中 architecture 是否确实写成 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，不要把无效轮次当结构证据。"],"reference_round":279}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0297.stdout.log:1541:research/history/logs/agent_round_0276.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s^{k1}(x)} α_{s,i}^{sh}(x) b_{s,i}^{sh} + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^{τ,k2}(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(r_sh(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 {B_s^sh} 是两个 always-on shared 静态子库，r_sh(x)=x-Σ_sΣ_i α_{s,i}^{sh}(x)b_{s,i}^{sh}，E_pk^*(·) 表示在 residual 上由 product-key router 按 token 难度自适应启用 1 或 2 个静态 expert 子库，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared coarse 子库查表 + residual 上的 PK 路由 + 少量 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，不依赖动态字典，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r275 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 切到新 family `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，在 exact 同成本 `total_cost_ratio=0.109375` 下引入 difficulty-aware variable-active cleanup path，能比固定 AE=2 的 dual-shared scaffold 更有效地处理 hard tokens，把 exceed_alpha_0.50 继续从 r275 的 `0.172059` 往下压，并争取逼近或击败 incumbent r266。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在同成本下明显优于 r275，并接近或击败 r266，则下一轮只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125`，测试在 adaptive cleanup 存在时是否重新回到更轻 coarse split 更优。","如果该 family 只比 r275 小幅更好但仍明显不够接近 incumbent，则记录为“variable-active path 有帮助，但不足以带来 regime shift”，后续应停止在 adaptive 邻域细扫。","如果该 family 不如 r275，则说明在当前 PK/shared scaffold 上 adaptive 1-or-2 expert path 不是主要突破口，后续应转向其他真正改变 cleanup 语义或 coarse 表达方式的新结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，真实改动文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","该 family 与 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 分支仍保持双 shared banks，但 routed cleanup 从固定 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 改为按 token 难度自适应启用 1 或 2 个 PK experts；与 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 容量从 1 个 shared bank 扩到 2 个。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, stage1_ratio=0.25, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=294912 (`0.0703125x`)、deployment_accesses=163840 (`0.0390625x`)、combined_accesses=458752 (`0.109375x`)；与 r274/r275 的 dual-shared fixed-AE scaffold 同档，因此这是一个干净的 matched architecture probe。","兼容性注册表已补充该 family，当前解析结果为 `direct_compatible`；更新后本地计数为直接兼容 14 个、扩展兼容 25 个、不兼容 3 个。","当前 dual-shared scaffold 已给出真实正向证据：r275 相对 r274 在同成本下把 exceed 从 `0.177462` 压到 `0.172059`，说明这条新 scaffold 仍值得一次 architecture-level upgrade，而不是继续做 split 邻域细扫。"],"reference_round":275,"self_review":"这轮符合当前阶段约束。最近两轮 r274-r275 都停留在同一 dual-shared family 内，且 objective 仍未接近 incumbent；按策略此时应优先换结构槽位，而不是继续补 `STAGE1_RATIO` 近邻点。选择 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 而不是继续在 dual-shared 上做 `0.125/0.375` 分裂点，是因为它直接测试当前高优先级方向“variable-active path by difficulty”，同时完全建立在已有 winning scaffold 的近同成本升级上。代码侧仅新增最小 family，并完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、override allowlist、compatibility registry 与 exact-string smoke；没有新增 tunable key，因此不需要改 `config_resolution`、`runner` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。主要风险是 adaptive active 在单-shared 版本上曾给过弱负信号；但 dual-shared scaffold 已把 coarse 主干抬强，当前最有价值的问题正是这是否能让 difficulty-aware cleanup 真正发挥作用。","summary":"已新增并接通 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r275 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，直接裁决“更厚 shared coarse 主干 + 按难度可变 1-or-2 PK cleanup path”能否在与 dual-shared fixed-AE 完全同成本的 `0.109375x` 档位继续显著压低 exceed。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
