caffold-level cleanup 升级，而不是继续在 residual 语义上细扫。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`，真实落盘文件仅有 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`。","该 family 与 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的精确差异不是新增库或改 K，而是把最后一段 tiny factorized residual cleanup 的系数形成方式从 plain ReLU top-k 改成 JumpReLU-gated residual selection；shared coarse 与 PK expert cleanup 语义保持不变。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=2048, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56, stage1_ratio=0.25, factorized_hidden_dim=256)` 在 CUDA 上可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 override allowlist 校验已通过：对 `ARCHITECTURE/K/EXPANSION_FACTOR/NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT/STAGE1_RATIO/FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM/OPTIMIZER/LR` 的完整 recipe，`validate_env_overrides(...) == []`。","本地成本自检已通过：`selection_accesses=325696`、`deployment_accesses=163840`、`combined_accesses=489536`、`exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625`，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","当前 recipe 下 residual hidden dim 实际被 `min(latents_per_expert, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM)` 裁到 `56`，因此该新 family 的精确成本与现有 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 同档，适合做 matched cleanup-semantics probe。"],"reference_round":282,"self_review":"这轮满足代码类变更约束：我先真实落盘了新 family，再返回 `edit_sae_code`。修改范围保持最小，只做了 architecture whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现和 override allowlist，没有新增 tunable env key，也没有改 launcher / controller 语义。主假设也保持单一：只回答“thresholded tail cleanup 语义是否比 plain residual 更能压 low-K exceed”。主要风险是 JumpReLU 可能过度抑制 tiny residual bank，导致 tail 容量反而下降；如果结果如此，就应停止继续在这一条 residual-tail 语义上细扫。","summary":"已实现并注册 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu_residual`。建议本轮以 r282 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，做一轮 shared+PK scaffold 上的 matched cleanup-semantics probe，直接判断 JumpReLU tail residual 能否在约 `0.1167x` 成本下把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 明显压低。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
