research/history/logs/agent_round_0297.stdout.log:1991:research/history/logs/agent_action_0288.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_1(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(r_2(x))} γ_m(x) c_m`，其中 `r_1(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^sh b_i^sh`，`r_2(x)=r_1(x)-Σ_{e,j} α_{e,j} b_{e,j}`。第一项是 always-on shared coarse 静态子库，第二项是在残差上由 product-key 选出的少量静态 expert 子库内的 JumpReLU cleanup，第三项是一个很小的 factorized global residual 静态库做 tail cleanup；在线链路仍是“shared 查表 -> residual -> PK expert 子库查表 -> residual -> tiny factorized residual 子库查表 -> 有限加权和”，不依赖动态字典，因此新 family `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 判定为扩展兼容。明确不兼容 family 仍只作历史参考，不得驱动当前兼容 leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：r283-r287 已基本否定现有 `shared+PK` 邻域里的 adaptive-active、dual-shared、residual-shared、shared-lowrank 与 plain-PK control，但这些失败主要说明旧 cleanup 语义没有形成 regime shift；当前更高信息量的问题是，在保留 winning scaffold `shared coarse + PK routed cleanup` 的前提下，额外加一个很小的全局 residual tail-cleanup 库，能否把 hard-token exceed 再压下去。新 family 相对现有 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异不是重命名，而是在 shared coarse 与 PK cleanup 之后新增一个 tiny factorized residual bank；它也不同于已失败的 `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，因为后者只是复用同一 PK expert 集做第二次 cleanup，而这里新增的是一个全局 residual 静态库。代码已实际落盘并完成 exact-string smoke 与 allowlist 自检；在当前 2048 many-tiny recipe `K=32, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 下，本地 exact 成本复核为 selection_accesses=325696、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=489536、exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625，仍处于 `0.08~0.14` 主战场并满足硬预算。若想击败当前 incumbent r282 objective≈0.268418，则需要把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到约 `0.151704` 以下。","summary":"已新增并接通 `shared_product_key_expert_residual`。建议以 r282 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_expert_residual`，在同一 2048 many-tiny scaffold 上做一轮新的 matched architecture probe，直接测试“shared coarse + PK routed cleanup + tiny global residual tail-cleanup”是否能在约 `0.1167x` 成本下更强地降低 exceed。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_product_key_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮符合当前策略约束。最近 5 轮都没有把 objective 拉过 r282，继续在已有 `shared+PK` 邻域做 `K/STAGE1_RATIO/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 近邻细扫已经明显低信息；而 plain PK、shared-lowrank、dual-shared、residual-dual-shared、shared adaptive-active 都给了更新且更直接的负信号。与其在这些已知弱槽位里继续补点，更有价值的是新开一个建立在 winning scaffold 之上的 cleanup 语义升级。代码改动限制在最小必要文件：`sparsify/config.py` whitelist、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch+实现、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py` allowlist、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md` compatibility 行；没有新增 tunable env key，因此不需要改 `controller.py`、`config_resolution.py` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。主要风险是新加的 tiny residual bank 会抬高 encoder cost，却换不回足够多的 exceed 改善；但这正是当前单目标下最值得一次性回答的结构问题，而且 exact cost 仍稳在可接受带内。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_product_key_expert_residual"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `shared_product_key_expert_residual`，真实改动文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","该 family 的精确结构语义是：保留 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的 shared coarse + PK expert cleanup，再追加一个 tiny factorized global residual cleanup；它不是 `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 或 `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的重命名。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='shared_product_key_expert_residual', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=2048, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56, stage1_ratio=0.25, factorized_hidden_dim=256)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 override allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'shared_product_key_expert_residual'}], fallback_architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=325696、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=489536、exact total_cost_ratio=0.1167144775390625；在当前 fused-QKV proxy 下满足硬预算。","兼容性表已补充该 family：`shared_product_key_expert_residual` 应按扩展兼容处理；当前 objective leaderboard 仍只比较兼容 family。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在约 `0.1167x` 下显著降低 exceed 并击败 r282，则下一轮继续留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，优先测试 shared coarse 与 tail-cleanup 的预算分配 knee。","如果该 family 只比 r284/r287 之类 shared-ordering 变体更好、但仍输给 r282，则说明新的全局 residual cleanup 语义有一定价值但不够形成 regime shift；后续可只保留一轮必要校准，否则应继续切换结构槽位。","如果该 family 与 r282 基本持平或更差，则可更明确地记录：当前 hookpoint 上额外的 tiny global residual bank 也不足以修复 low-K tail，之后应下调这类“shared+PK 后接轻 residual”方向的优先级。"],"reference_round":282}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0297.stdout.log:1992:research/history/logs/agent_round_0293.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"扩展兼容新结构 probe：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual` 的最终重构为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r1(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(r2(x))} γ_m c_m，其中 r1(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh b_i^sh，r2(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh b_i^sh-Σ α_{e,j} b_{e,j}。shared coarse、adaptive PK expert cleanup 与 residual cleanup 都落在静态向量库上，在线侧仍是 LUTurbo/Lottable 可导出的查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿流水线，因此兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 cleanup scaffold 上加入 difficulty-aware adaptive-active expert path，能比固定 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 更强地降低 hard-token exceed，而 cost proxy 基本不变。","summary":"已实际新增并集成 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，只在 `sparsify/` 落盘修改 whitelist 与 runtime dispatch/class implementation。该 family 复用 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 shared + PK + residual scaffold，仅把 expert cleanup 改成 adaptive-active 选择。按本地 smoke 与 cost 估计，在继承 r282 的 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 配置下 total_cost_ratio 仍约 `0.12x`，与 r288/r292 同量级；这使本轮成为一个纯粹检验“variable-active cleanup 是否能显著压低 exceed”的 matched-cost architecture probe。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这是一次有信息增量的新结构 probe，而不是继续扫已平台化的 split 邻域。风险在于 cost proxy 不会奖励 adaptive-active 的轻路径，所以若 exceed 改善不够，这条线可能仍输给 incumbent；但它正面回答了当前最高价值的问题：在保留 shared+PK+residual scaffold 的同时，difficulty-aware cleanup 是否值得继续。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["已落盘新增 family：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，并完成 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch/class 接线。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计：selection_ratio≈0.08，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.12；与 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 同量级，适合作为 matched-cost exceed probe。","该 family 的结构语义是：shared coarse 吃主干，adaptive-active PK experts 按难度做 cleanup，最后 tiny residual head 做全局 tail cleanup；兼容性应视为扩展兼容。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮 exceed 明显低于 r288/r292 且 objective 接近或优于 incumbent，再以该 family 为 anchor 做一次最小 knee 校准，例如 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或 residual split。","若本轮 objective 仍无改善，则可将‘adaptive-active + residual cleanup’这条线一并降级，后续应转向真正不同的 coarse/shared 表达方式，而不是继续在 PK cleanup 语义上叠层。","若本轮出现 sanity 或 registration 异常，优先把它当新 family 集成问题处理，并用同一 exact architecture string 重做 smoke/dispatch 检查。"],"reference_round":282}
