research/history/logs/agent_round_0293.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"扩展兼容新结构 probe：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual` 的最终重构为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r1(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(r2(x))} γ_m c_m，其中 r1(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh b_i^sh，r2(x)=x-Σ α_i^sh b_i^sh-Σ α_{e,j} b_{e,j}。shared coarse、adaptive PK expert cleanup 与 residual cleanup 都落在静态向量库上，在线侧仍是 LUTurbo/Lottable 可导出的查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿流水线，因此兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 cleanup scaffold 上加入 difficulty-aware adaptive-active expert path，能比固定 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 更强地降低 hard-token exceed，而 cost proxy 基本不变。","summary":"已实际新增并集成 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，只在 `sparsify/` 落盘修改 whitelist 与 runtime dispatch/class implementation。该 family 复用 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的 shared + PK + residual scaffold，仅把 expert cleanup 改成 adaptive-active 选择。按本地 smoke 与 cost 估计，在继承 r282 的 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 配置下 total_cost_ratio 仍约 `0.12x`，与 r288/r292 同量级；这使本轮成为一个纯粹检验“variable-active cleanup 是否能显著压低 exceed”的 matched-cost architecture probe。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这是一次有信息增量的新结构 probe，而不是继续扫已平台化的 split 邻域。风险在于 cost proxy 不会奖励 adaptive-active 的轻路径，所以若 exceed 改善不够，这条线可能仍输给 incumbent；但它正面回答了当前最高价值的问题：在保留 shared+PK+residual scaffold 的同时，difficulty-aware cleanup 是否值得继续。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["已落盘新增 family：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual`，并完成 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch/class 接线。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_residual` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计：selection_ratio≈0.08，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.12；与 `shared_product_key_expert_residual` 同量级，适合作为 matched-cost exceed probe。","该 family 的结构语义是：shared coarse 吃主干，adaptive-active PK experts 按难度做 cleanup，最后 tiny residual head 做全局 tail cleanup；兼容性应视为扩展兼容。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮 exceed 明显低于 r288/r292 且 objective 接近或优于 incumbent，再以该 family 为 anchor 做一次最小 knee 校准，例如 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或 residual split。","若本轮 objective 仍无改善，则可将‘adaptive-active + residual cleanup’这条线一并降级，后续应转向真正不同的 coarse/shared 表达方式，而不是继续在 PK cleanup 语义上叠层。","若本轮出现 sanity 或 registration 异常，优先把它当新 family 集成问题处理，并用同一 exact architecture string 重做 smoke/dispatch 检查。"],"reference_round":282}
