research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:4212:research/history/logs/agent_action_0281.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = sum_{i in S_sh(x)} a_i^sh b_i^sh + sum_{e in E_pk(r1(x))} sum_{j in S_e^tau(r1(x))} beta_{e,j} c_{e,j} + sum_{e in E_pk(r1(x))} sum_{m in S_e^tau(r2(x))} gamma_{e,m} c_{e,m}`，其中 `r1(x)=x-shared(x)`，`r2(x)=r1(x)-cleanup1(x)`；shared coarse 子库 `{b_i^sh}` 与 routed expert 子库 `{c_{e,*}}` 都是静态向量库，第二次 cleanup 复用第一次 PK 选出的同一批静态 expert 子库，只是在更小 residual 上再做一次 expert-local JumpReLU 系数计算，因此在线导出仍是 LUTurbo/Lottable 可执行的“shared 查表 + PK 选子库 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判断为直接兼容。它与现有 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异不是换名字，而是在不增加 deployment K 的前提下，把 routed cleanup 从单次变成同一 expert set 上的两次 residual cleanup；它也不同于 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，因为新增深度发生在 PK expert cleanup 内，而不是 shared bank 串联。相对 r266 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，保持 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, adam, LR=8e-4` 不变，直接回答“在当前 winning scaffold 上，用更强 hard-token cleanup 语义而非更大 shared/coarse 或更轻 factorized head，能否以近同部署成本明显压低 exceed_alpha_0.50”。本地精确成本复核显示该新 family 的 `selection_accesses=352256, deployment_accesses=163840, combined_accesses=516096, exact total_cost_ratio=0.123046875`；要打赢 r266 的 exact objective≈0.275001，只需把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到约 `0.15195` 以下。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在约 0.123x 下把 exceed 明显压到 0.15 左右或更低，下一轮继续留在该 family，只做一次最小的 `STAGE1_RATIO` follow-up，确认 shared/coarse 与 stacked cleanup 的预算分配 knee。","如果该 family 只带来很小 exceed 改善，说明当前瓶颈不在“同一 expert set 的更深 cleanup”，后续应停止继续堆 PK cleanup 深度，转去别的 scaffold 升级槽位。","如果该 family 有清晰正信号但交换率仍不够，下一步更值得测试的是在该语义上叠加更厚 coarse scaffold，而不是回到 hash 或 factorized expert heads。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 f